name: Assteroid
description: assteroid, one of a kind shape orbiting in the Solar System, has been a widely used meme for over a decade. From smashing the icy cold giant twice billions of years ago to constant news reports of a potential to hit the Earth - the little hot rock has one kind of a job. Its name, bringing up the smile on everyone's face, from a mix of intended mispronunciation and human immaturity has cemented its place in the internet culture.
